CHAT.comment: To Brittany , I want to go back to Arizona again! I Liked it a_lot out ther! Love , Chi (first name)

Context notes say Chi lies on floor and kicks feet about as she writes (a girl after my own heart). Chi is left- handed. The letter is to a friend who I think is at Chi's school but Chi writes about going back to Arizona , where Chi and Mot had visited recently. The idea that EXP will keep the letter is very strong , and Mot mentions that they can write a real letter after the visit is over. Chi mouths words to herself to spell them , and she does a pretty good job. Chi comes up with the content of the letter , and Mot helps with spelling and punctuation.

u.a: writes a comma somewhere other than on the letter
draws ay on paper with finger
